Item 8.	Financial Statements and Supplementary Data
The following financial statements and supplementary data are hereby incorporated by reference to pages 7 to 15 of the Company's Annual Report.
(i) Consolidated Balance Sheets at January 28, 1995 and January 29, 1994;
(ii) Consolidated Statements of Earnings for each of the three years in the period ended January 28, 1995;
(iii) Consolidated Statements of Cash Flows for each of the three years in the period ended January 28, 1995;
(iv) Consolidated Statements of Stockholders' Equity for each of the three years in the period ended January 28, 1995;
(v) Notes to Consolidated Financial Statements; and
(vi) Opinion of Ernst & Young LLP.
Individual financial statements of the registrant's subsidiaries are not furnished because consolidated financial statements are furnished. The registrant is primarily an operating company and all subsidiaries are at least 80% owned.
Financial statements of 50%-owned joint ventures are not submitted because such companies, considered in the aggregate, are not considered a significant subsidiary as defined in Regulation S-X.
